val requiredColumns = List("title", "breadCrumbs", "categoryNamePath", "categoryNamePath_status", "title_status", "breadCrumbs_status")
val columns = spotCheckingData.head().toSeq.map(x => if (x == null) "null" else x.toString).zipWithIndex
.filter(x => requiredColumns.contains(x._1)).map(x => ("_c" + (x._2), x._1)).toList

val actualColumns = columns.map(x => x._1)
val newColumns = columns.map(x => x._2)
val spotCheckData = spotCheckingData.select(actualColumns.head, actualColumns.tail: _*).toDF(newColumns: _*).filter($"_c26" !== "title")

result.msg:

paragraphs.text:
val clfnSpotCheckResults = sqlContext.sql("select categoryNamePath_status, COUNT(categoryNamePath_status) from spotcheckdata where not(isnull(categoryNamePath_status)) GROUP BY categoryNamePath_status")
                            .collect().map(_.toSeq).map(x => (x(0), x(1).asInstanceOf[Long])).toMap
                            
//Misclassified
clfnSpotCheckResults("Incorrect")

result.msg: What is probability of misclassifying a sample?

paragraphs.text:

// probability 
clfnSpotCheckResults("Incorrect") * 1.0 / (clfnSpotCheckResults("Incorrect") + clfnSpotCheckResults("Correct"))

%sql select topCategoryOf(categoryNamePath) as topCategory, COUNT(topCategoryOf(categoryNamePath)) count
from spotcheckdata where not(isnull(breadCrumbs_status)) and not(isnull(categoryNamePath_status)) and breadCrumbs_status != "Correct" and categoryNamePath_status == "Correct" GROUP BY topCategoryOf(categoryNamePath)
